# Comparelo – Multi-Platform Product Price Comparison System

## Overview

Comparelo is a web-based product comparison platform designed to simplify online shopping by allowing users to compare product prices from multiple retailers within a single interface.

The system eliminates the need to manually browse multiple e-commerce websites by automatically retrieving product information from various retailers, processing the data, and presenting the most relevant comparison results to the user.

The platform focuses on improving consumer decision-making through real-time price comparison, centralized product information, and direct redirection to retailer websites.

