## System Architecture

```text
User
 │
 ▼
Search Product
 │
 ▼
Data Collection Layer
 │
 ├── Amazon Scraper
 ├── Flipkart Scraper
 └── Myntra Integration
 │
 ▼
Data Processing
 │
 ├── Filtering
 ├── Normalization
 └── Price Sorting
 │
 ▼
Comparison Engine
 │
 ▼
Result Display
 │
 ▼
Retailer Redirection
```

---

## Workflow

### Phase 1: User Interaction

- User visits website
- User enters product details

### Phase 2: Data Gathering

- Query product information
- Retrieve retailer data
- Store product information

### Phase 3: Data Processing

- Normalize collected data
- Filter results
- Sort products by price

### Phase 4: Comparison Display

- Generate comparison results
- Display retailer prices
- Show product information

### Phase 5: Purchase Redirection

- User selects preferred retailer
- System redirects user to retailer website

This workflow was implemented based on the project architecture described in the technical documentation. :contentReference[oaicite:8]{index=8}

