---

## Backend API Endpoints

### Login

```http
POST /login
```

Authenticate users using email and password.

### Compare Products

```http
POST /compare
```

Returns sorted product comparisons from multiple retailers.

### Retailer Redirect

```http
POST /redirect
```

Redirects users to the selected retailer's website. :contentReference[oaicite:9]{index=9}

