## Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Sneha-Vasudev/Comparelo.git
cd Comparelo
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Run Application

```bash
python comparelo_backend.py
```

Server starts at:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

